#+title: linux notes

to have picom autostart put this is *~/.xinitrc:*
picom ~/.config/picom &

for remapping caps lock to control in X11 sessions, shove this into the xinitrc/xmodmap:
Xmodmap:
clear lock
clear control
keycode 66 = Control_L
add control = Control_L
add Lock = Control_R

and then the xinitrc:
xmodmap ~/.Xmodmap

git from command line:
git init
git config --global user.name "git name"
git config --global user.email my@email.com

Once logged in simply:
git add .
git commit -m 'commit message'
git push
